{"tid":1953912,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"傳統車牌轉讓問題","createTime":"2020-04-01T12:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T05:17:38.000Z","uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"977e9187dac210cefef71d6a05425627d5c123e3","tid":1953912,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eqNtgGJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeqNtgGJ.jpg&h=9c9e1ae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟勾左個車牌 但想俾我屋企人架車用架車唔係我名<br />\n係咪唔可以就可俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5e4ce37579223967dd539d468d8a825f1ec4fd","tid":1953912,"uid":152029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:40:10.000Z","msg":"係咪要套左我我名架車先再可以做留牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd4726563d47e5a860a9fda85a436c4ea6fa292","tid":1953912,"uid":704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"搵牌佬搞"},{"pid":"95f61cf5dc1887756cf86aeee39e7e0ec6490887","tid":1953912,"uid":152029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6dd4726563d47e5a860a9fda85a436c4ea6fa292","tid":1953912,"uid":704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"搵牌佬搞"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"搵牌佬搞詳情係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我見封信話要套我登記名下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b325ffc4cf6365a82f2a4aa43a09e521fe0fe4","tid":1953912,"uid":58409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"架車要轉你個名"},{"pid":"a5fd3610dba9b64d82ccc93ff73941792e1db9a1","tid":1953912,"uid":28505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T13:28:25.000Z","msg":"牌佬會轉架電單車俾你<br />\